pgTitle: List of RAF aircrew in the Battle of Britain (V–Z)

rows.text: ||KIA 12 October 1940 aged 21 as a Pilot of Hurricane V7426 which was shot down by Bf 109s over Hastings and crashed near Cranbrook.
||MIA 31 July 1940 aged 24 following a collision between Blenheims L6722 and L1408 over the Bristol Channel.
||KIA 25 August 1940 when his Hurricane V7250 was shot down inflames over Portland.
||KIFA when aircraft ran out of fuel at sea between HMS Argus and Malta (transfer to 261 Sqn), 16 November 1940, aged 20. Robert J. Boret died in the same incident.
||KIFA 4 August 1940 when his Spitfire N3271 spun into the ground during dog fight training.
||KIA 18 October 1940 when his Hurricane P3872 crashed during an attempted forced landing on return from a patrol in bad weather.
||KIA 8 October 1940 when he was killed following a bale out from his Spitfire N3043 which was shot down in combat with Bf 109s over Kent.
BR Listed on CWGC website as Australian
Taken POW 26 August 1940 but escaped. Died May 1987
||MIA 16 August 1940 when he failed to return in his Spitfire R6802 after combat with Bf 109s.
||KIA 8 August 1940 when Blenheim L8665 was shot down in flames into the sea near Ramsgate, Kent.
||KIA 31 August 1940 when his Spitfire X4273 was shot down by Bf 109s over London.
||KIA 13 July 1940 when his Spitfire R6807 crashed during a routine patrol, cause not known.
||MIA 11 September 1940 when his Blenheim was shot down by Bf 109s and crashed into the sea.
||KIA 25 July 1940 when his Spitfire R6707 crashed into the sea following combat with a Bf 109.
MIA 7 November 1940 (his brother Maj. Adrian John Anthony Weir MC was also KIA)
||MIA 25 August 1940 when he failed to return in Spitfire R6966 after combat with Bf 109s over Canterbury.
||MIA 25 August 1940 when he failed to return in Spitfire R6994 from combat over the channel.;
||MIA 25 August 1940 after Hurricane R4199 crashed near Portland after being badly damaged in a head-on attack with a Bf 110.
Retired as AVM in 1963. Died 14 January 1988
Retired as Air Cdre in 1973; died 5 November 2007
